headline: Dell (DELL) Stock Trades Up, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of computer hardware and IT solutions company Dell (NYSE:DELL) jumped 2.8% in the afternoon session after investor optimism grew around the company's performance in the artificial intelligence (AI) hardware market, supported by a broader rally in technology stocks.

headline: Trump Says Murdochs, Dell Likely Part of Group Buying TikTok in the US
summary: President Donald Trump said that Rupert Murdoch and his son Lachlan Murdoch, as well as Dell CEO Michael Dell, may be involved in the group buying Chinese-owned TikTok’s U.S operations.

headline: Is Dell Poised for More Growth After OpenAI’s $100B AI Infrastructure News?
